@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.69 / v2 + 1.00) - v1) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.90 / tmp + 0.61)))
    tmp = (tmp / wp.sin((v2 + 0.48 * v2 + 0.52)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.93 / tmp + 0.84)) - wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.18)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (v0 / 0.00)
    data[tid] = v0
